  <brief_title>Effect of Hydrocortisone on Improving Outcome of Pneumatic Reduction of Infantile Intussusception</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Hydrocortisone on Improving Outcome of Pneumatic Reduction of Infantile Intussusception: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
